data.description: Welcome home to affordable and spacious living in this 3-story townhouse with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms plus 2 half bathrooms, and single car garage just over 2,000 total square feet in the sought-after Chaddsford community. This enchanting interior features 9 ft. high ceilings, and has many features that will make you question waiting for new construction. Enter your new home from the lower level or your front facing garage and be greeted by hardwood floors, plenty of space to relax in a TV room or Den before heading upstairs. The carpeted stairs lead to the Main level of the home featuring easy maintenance hardwood floors, a half bath, and recessed lighting in the kitchen and dining room. Top of the line black sleek GE appliances in the gourmet kitchen are in this exquisite, modern, kitchen with an oversized island and quartz countertops. Also enjoy the electric fireplace in the living room and the wall unit fireplace in the basement. Entertain guests in your spacious living room or back deck right off the kitchen. Take the last flight of steps to the final floor and find wall-to-wall carpets in each of the three spacious bedrooms with the Private Suite being opposite the other two bedrooms for extra privacy. Laundry is a breeze with the laundry room being conveniently located on the upper level for easy living. The primary suite is an oasis featuring a large walk-in closet, tiled bathroom with soak tub and shower combo, his and hers sinks, and a large mirror to check yourself once more before heading to start your day. Located in the Chaddsford community, you will have access to many amenities which include a pool, a clubhouse, parks, playgrounds, tennis and basketball courts, and walking trails. You'll also find yourself in close proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment, Route 301, Andrews Airforce Base, and the Beltway.  Seller help is available.
